  "name": "Clopidogrel Poor Metabolizers - Comprehensive Provider Query",
  "description": "Provider-level query for clopidogrel poor metabolizers per PheKB VESPA algorithm — patients on clopidogrel who experience adverse cardiovascular events (MI). The intersection (not just union) defines putative poor metabolizers.",
  "prompt": "Find clopidogrel-treated patients who experienced acute myocardial infarction — putative clopidogrel poor metabolizers per the VESPA algorithm.",
  "prompts": {
    "naive": "Find clopidogrel patients with MI.",
    "broad": "Find clopidogrel-treated patients with subsequent acute myocardial infarction — the case definition for clopidogrel poor metabolizers in the PheKB VESPA pharmacogenetic study.",
    "expert": "Run two queries. (1) MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|32968 — clopidogrel. (2) Condition?code=http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|I21.9,http://snomed.info/sct|22298006 — AMI dx. Patients with both are putative poor metabolizers."
  },
